Introduction

My name is Shahnawaz Hossan. I am a passionate Software Engineer(Full Stack). Currently I am working as a Full-Stack Software Engineer for a Software Company. I believe that sheer determination, dedication and hard working capacity will help me to reach the pinnacle in the development, computing and research field.

I used to write on different programming topics in my native language during my competitive programming. This is my site. I've written about various types of programming topics like number theory, bit manipulation, data structures, sorting etc. After starting my career, I have faced many types of problems during my development and research. That's why I started this website so that I can share those solutions of problems I faced with everyone.


Programming Career

I was a competitive programmer during my university time. I have solved 1000+ programming problems on different online judges. These are my profiles:

      UVa
      Codeforces
      HackerRank
      LightOJ
      CSAcademy

Alongside problem solving, I participated in various programming contests below:

      National Collegiate Programming Contest (NCPC) at University of Asia Pacific – 2016
      Inter University Programming Contest at State University Bangladesh – 2016
      Inter University Programming Contest at State University Bangladesh – 2015
      Inter University Programming Contest at BUET – 2015
      IUT 7 th National ICT FEST – 2015
      IUT 6 th National ICT FEST – 2014
